{
  "texts": [
    "Although the ARIMA model showed a slight increase in prediction accuracy compared to the ARMA model, it still had a linear graph.",
    "The resulting RMSE, MAE, and MAPE scores are lower than those of the ARMA model.",
    "However, when the SARIMA model is applied, the results showed a better prediction accuracy than both the ARMA and ARIMA models, with a graph that is trending upwards, in line with the actual data.",
    "Furthermore, the resulting RMSE, MAE, and MAPE scores are 5197.89, 4194.04, and 0.12, respectively, which are lower than the scores of the other models.",
    "Therefore, the SARIMA model is selected for future revenue predictions based on plan subscriptions for the company."
  ]
}